{
  "stem": "13874.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I come to ascend-- a lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the way I got that, you said where-- where through France?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went all the way through France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were flown into Passau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After that, took the northerly route across the Rhine and [NON-ENGLISH] through the northern part of Germany-- Hildesheim and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wound up in Mecklenburg, across the Elbe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was one of the troops across-- who got across the Elbe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on, that territory had to be ceded to the Russian advancing troops.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And three weeks before the armistice, our division was for the first time put back in the reserve.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's where finally, the papers for my commission caught up with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was made a lieutenant three weeks before the war ended.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had two.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The enlisted man serial number was 32468061, and the officer's one was 2015956.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a pleasure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was great-- great satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not so much about interrogation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- as I said, it was routine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a few run-ins with somebody, but that's--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was prisoners who didn't want to talk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I convinced them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said I was the boss-- very fast interrogation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it's not that much to brag about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But one thing I wanted to talk about is I mentioned that we were put-- during the armistice, we were in the reserve-- pulled back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just had gotten my commission.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And shortly-- when we were used to go to prisoner of war camps, and sort out and release them by-- released some Germans back to their hometowns-- and while I was on that duty, by divisions of the 5th infantry division was put out to be shipped to Japan.",
      "word_count": 49
    }
  ],
